        {
            "title": "華勤技術IPO在港售股超購530倍 1手中籤率12% 股份今登場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華勤技術(03296)將於今日掛牌，公司昨公布認購結果，在港公開發售部份獲531.33倍認購，1手中籤率12%；國際配售認購則為13.34倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華勤技術官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260331_FI_source-web_603296-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華勤技術官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260331_FI_source-web_603296-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華勤技術官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股昨天暗盤亦高收，輝立交易平台顯示的暗盤收市價94元，較招股價77.7元高21%；富途交易平台則顯示該股暗盤收報91.15元，高於招股價17.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909106-%e8%8f%af%e5%8b%a4%e6%8a%80%e8%a1%93ipo%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e5%94%ae%e8%82%a1%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc530%e5%80%8d-1%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%8712-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e4%bb%8a%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/03296.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 09:05:04",
